00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:13,000
So I made my masks initially with the GFP channel.

79
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:26,000
But then I said, hey, Cellpose, I would like you to train a custom model based on the nuclear channel and the nuclear channel masks.

