00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,000
Tricky.

81
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:44,000
I can try to get Cellpose to learn to use this really dim signal that's in the DNA channel since it's present in both conditions to learn my cell mask from only the DNA.

